{"tid":2426076,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港抗爭布條高雄展出 陳其邁撐場","createTime":"2021-02-27T18:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T03:18:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e06e8a4bd5631ee62744e78837f4a18515156d","tid":2426076,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T18:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_uFmL2xOf3YEac3lm2cZxK_a-pY=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HOO2KMMRBJHBRAUYIH2MXLNAO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_uFmL2xOf3YEac3lm2cZxK_a-pY%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHOO2KMMRBJHBRAUYIH2MXLNAO4.jpg&h=b7b9d3b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HzPDNxm8O--hJgmZX2N0ofuh2Ds=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6MKSZPNNSBEPHICRK6ODEJMHCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHzPDNxm8O--hJgmZX2N0ofuh2Ds%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6MKSZPNNSBEPHICRK6ODEJMHCY.jpg&h=ad5b1b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動將滿兩周年，高雄駁二藝術特區推出「若水，如火，有聲：一個關於行動的展覽」及「返校Detention實境體驗展」。高雄市長陳其邁昨日特意前來參觀，並表示「這兩個展，一個是敍述香港爭取自由民主的現在式，一個則以實演方式呈現台灣過去白色恐怖歷史，都呈現了自由民主的價值。」陳更在連儂牆寫下「KH撐HK、香港加油」。<br />\n<br />\n「敍述港人不屈不撓」<br />\n<br />\n「一個關於行動的展覽」展出了抗爭現場、新聞攝影、藝術創作到出版紀錄等港台創作逾百件作品，更首次完整展開當時長40公尺的抗爭布條，陳其邁表示，有關展覽是在敍述港人爭取自由，他們不屈不撓的抗爭，但是也面臨包括國安法，或者是其他對香港人權自由的打壓。<br />\n<br />\n展覽現場完整呈現來自香港反送中運動現場的40公尺大型布條，陳更特地用便利貼親筆寫下「KH撐HK、香港加油」貼在連儂牆上，並強調「做為一個自由人，做為一個高雄人，除了要珍惜得來不易的民主自由，其實可以來這裏看看，看在我們近水之隔、隔壁的香港正在發生哪些事情，讓我們能夠一起來支持香港的民主，一起來撐香港。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210228/ENXJUH5AKJDRBAENURFRDRBV7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210228%2FENXJUH5AKJDRBAENURFRDRBV7M%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3ife5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=5460615a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210228%2FENXJUH5AKJDRBAENURFRDRBV7M%2F&h=64d29a76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210228/ENXJUH5AKJDRBAENURFRDRBV7M/</a>"},{"pid":"a6fbc4ec552dfeddbbc5fa80ba05077a58e36456","tid":2426076,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T18:57:03.000Z","msg":"KMT 人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩黨共識撚？"},{"pid":"40aacc73d70fbe895403286e5c25b419e68dc5d3","tid":2426076,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6fbc4ec552dfeddbbc5fa80ba05077a58e36456","tid":2426076,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T18:57:03.000Z","msg":"KMT 人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩黨共識撚？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T19:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />米分化"},{"pid":"1d8d6b489a86926b533670814275a6497ac7fab4","tid":2426076,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T00:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066459bf026719ab9923f9cd5354e54409ec88ce","tid":2426076,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T00:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3548b7fe46e89802a08def0b11a549c36e7d6